{{ 'policy-page.css' | asset_url | stylesheet_tag }}

<div class="policy-page bg-white">

  <div class="policy-layout">

    <div class="policy-prose">

      <div class="rp-highlights">
        <p class="rp-highlights__eyebrow">The quick version</p>
        <ul class="rp-highlights__list">
          <li>30-day money-back guarantee on most orders</li>
          <li>1–2 year limited warranty (varies by product)</li>
          <li>Free replacement on approved warranty claims</li>
          <li>Email <a href="mailto:support@ezq.com">support@ezq.com</a> to start a return or claim</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="rp-highlights__note">This is a summary. Full terms below.</p>
      </div>

      <h2 id="rp-money-back">30-Day Money Back Guarantee</h2>
      <p>Undamaged products can be returned for a full refund within 30 days of purchase. Refund requests under the 30-day money back guarantee must be submitted within 30 days of the original purchase date.</p>
      <p>Bulk orders of 10 or more units of the same product are not eligible for refund.</p>

      <h2 id="rp-condition">Product Condition Requirements</h2>
      <p>To qualify for a return, products must meet the following conditions:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Products with visible wear, damage, or signs of use are not eligible for return</li>
        <li>Returns must include all original accessories</li>
        <li>All returned items must be in original packaging</li>
        <li>Free gifts are not eligible for return</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 id="rp-how-to-return">How to Return an Item</h2>
      <p>To initiate a return, log into <a href="{{ routes.account_login_url }}">your account</a> or email <a href="mailto:support@ezq.com">support@ezq.com</a> with your order number. We respond within 24 business hours.</p>
      <p>If you checked out as a guest, register for an account using the same email address used at purchase to access your order history.</p>

      <h2 id="rp-cancel">Canceling an Order</h2>
      <p>You can cancel your order within one hour of placing it through <a href="{{ routes.account_login_url }}">your account</a>. After one hour, contact <a href="mailto:support@ezq.com">support@ezq.com</a>. Orders that have entered the shipping phase cannot be canceled.</p>

      <h2 id="rp-refund-processing">Refund Processing</h2>
      <p>Refunds are issued once the returned item arrives at our warehouse and passes inspection. The refund will be credited to the original payment method. Processing typically takes 3–5 business days.</p>

      <h2 id="rp-warranty">Warranty Claims for Quality-Related Issues</h2>
      <p>All quality-related defects on items sold directly by EZQuest are covered by a limited warranty starting from the date of purchase. Warranty periods vary by product (1–2 years). EZQuest's limited warranty applies in the country of original purchase.</p>
      <p>For approved warranty claims, replacement items will be provided as follows:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>A factory-refurbished product of equal value when available</li>
        <li>If no refurbished model is available, a new item will be sent</li>
      </ul>
      <p>Replacement products may differ in appearance or features from the original. EZQuest determines the most comparable replacement at its discretion.</p>
      <p>Replacement product warranties remain valid for the longer of:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>The original warranty period remaining for the defective item</li>
        <li>Three months from the date of replacement</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 id="rp-warranty-process">Warranty Claim Process</h2>
      <ol>
        <li><strong>Email or use the support form</strong> — Email <a href="mailto:support@ezq.com">support@ezq.com</a> or use the support form at <a href="/pages/contact">/pages/contact</a>. We respond within 24 business hours.</li>
        <li><strong>Try self-troubleshoot first</strong> — Many issues resolve with the <a href="/pages/support">Smart Help Center</a> — save time on round trips.</li>
        <li><strong>Gather your documentation</strong> — You'll need proof of purchase, the product's serial number, and photos or video showing the defect.</li>
        <li><strong>We review your claim</strong> — Approved claims receive a refurbished or new replacement shipped at no cost.</li>
        <li><strong>In some cases</strong>, the item may need to be returned for quality inspection before a replacement is issued.</li>
      </ol>

      <h2 id="rp-proof">Valid Proof of Purchase</h2>
      <p>A valid proof of purchase is required for all warranty claims. Accepted forms include:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Order number and original shipping address for online purchases on EZQuest</li>
        <li>A sales invoice with seller's name and the EZQuest product</li>
        <li>A dated sales receipt from an authorized EZQuest reseller showing the product description and purchase price</li>
      </ul>
      <p>Warranty claims must be submitted within 90 days of discovering the defect, and within the original warranty period (1–2 years depending on product).</p>

      <h2 id="rp-not-covered">Not Covered Under Warranty</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Normal aging or wear from regular use (including battery capacity reduction and color changes over time)</li>
        <li>Products without valid proof of purchase</li>
        <li>Lost or stolen items</li>
        <li>Products outside the warranty period</li>
        <li>Non-quality-related issues reported more than 30 days after purchase</li>
        <li>Free products or promotional giveaways</li>
        <li>Repairs or modifications performed by third parties</li>
        <li>Damage from external factors</li>
        <li>Damage from misuse (drops, extreme temperatures, liquid damage, improper operation)</li>
        <li>Products purchased from unauthorized resellers</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 id="rp-modification">Unauthorized Modification &amp; Warranty Limitation</h2>
      <p>Damage or malfunction caused by unauthorized repair, disassembly, modification, or use of non-approved parts is not covered by this Limited Warranty.</p>
      <p>This Limited Warranty does not affect your statutory rights under applicable consumer protection laws.</p>

      <h2 id="rp-liability">Liability Limitations</h2>
      <p>EZQuest is not liable for:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Loss of data resulting from product use</li>
        <li>Accidental returns made by the buyer</li>
        <li>Returning personal or unrelated items</li>
        <li>Costs from unauthorized returns (outside the approved warranty process)</li>
        <li>Any losses caused by misuse of the product</li>
      </ul>
      <p>Compensation, if applicable, will not exceed the original purchase price.</p>
      <p>The warranty policy may be updated based on legal requirements, internal company policies, or product revisions. This warranty policy applies only to products purchased through official EZQuest channels. Products bought from unauthorized sellers are not covered. EZQuest reserves the right to interpret and modify this policy.</p>
      <p>Mystery box promotions and early-bird campaigns are governed by their own terms and are not eligible for the general no-questions-asked return policy.</p>
      <p>For non-quality-related returns, the buyer is responsible for any damage or loss during transit. EZQuest does not offer refunds for items damaged in transit under non-quality-related warranty claims.</p>
      <p>If return items are shipped using a prepaid label provided by EZQuest as instructed, EZQuest will cover any loss or damage during transit. However, EZQuest is not responsible for returns involving altered labels, incorrect items, or empty packages, and no refund will be issued in such cases.</p>
      <p>For a list of authorized dealers and distributors, refer to our <a href="/pages/where-to-buy">where to buy</a> page.</p>

      <div class="rp-bottom-cta">
        <p>Have a question?</p>
        <a href="/pages/contact" class="btn btn--primary">Contact support</a>
      </div>

    </div>

    <aside class="policy-sidebar">

      <div class="policy-sidebar__card">
        <p class="policy-sidebar__label">In this document</p>
        <nav class="policy-sidebar__nav" aria-label="Jump to section">
          <a href="#rp-money-back" class="policy-sidebar__link">30-Day Money Back Guarantee</a>
          <a href="#rp-condition" class="policy-sidebar__link">Product Condition Requirements</a>
          <a href="#rp-how-to-return" class="policy-sidebar__link">How to Return an Item</a>
          <a href="#rp-cancel" class="policy-sidebar__link">Canceling an Order</a>
          <a href="#rp-refund-processing" class="policy-sidebar__link">Refund Processing</a>
          <a href="#rp-warranty" class="policy-sidebar__link">Warranty Claims</a>
          <a href="#rp-warranty-process" class="policy-sidebar__link">Warranty Claim Process</a>
          <a href="#rp-proof" class="policy-sidebar__link">Valid Proof of Purchase</a>
          <a href="#rp-not-covered" class="policy-sidebar__link">Not Covered Under Warranty</a>
          <a href="#rp-modification" class="policy-sidebar__link">Unauthorized Modification</a>
          <a href="#rp-liability" class="policy-sidebar__link">Liability Limitations</a>
        </nav>
      </div>

      <div class="policy-sidebar__card policy-sidebar__card--help">
        <p class="policy-sidebar__help-title">Start a return or claim</p>
        <p class="policy-sidebar__help-body">
          Email <a href="mailto:support@ezq.com">support@ezq.com</a> with your order number. We respond within 24 business hours.
        </p>
        <a href="/pages/contact"
           class="btn btn--primary"
           style="display:block;text-align:center;margin-top:1rem;border-radius:100px">
          Contact support
        </a>
      </div>

      <div class="policy-sidebar__card">
        <p class="policy-sidebar__label">Related</p>
        <nav class="policy-sidebar__nav">
          <a href="/pages/warranty" class="policy-sidebar__link">Warranty overview</a>
          <a href="/pages/shipping-returns" class="policy-sidebar__link">Shipping &amp; returns</a>
          <a href="/pages/support" class="policy-sidebar__link">Support center</a>
          <a href="/pages/where-to-buy" class="policy-sidebar__link">Where to buy</a>
        </nav>
      </div>

    </aside>
  </div>

</div>

<style>
